{"id":670517,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":11}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"99","ytitle":"","mtitle":"春天的“白天鹅”","ftitle":"","authors":["王林"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了寻找蓝色的湖泊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你驾着白云从南国飞来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羽翅上载着温暖的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福我辽阔豪爽的北方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我的心也高高飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追随你去找友谊和希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到春天走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘着绿色的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海在汹涌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪尖闪耀理想之光……"}]}